{"tid":1546251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復香港」係日常問候語！","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T16:02:25.000Z","uid":184233,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d250c2c98b43d41ff14897eff288f4b0c9e9ee8a","tid":1546251,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"要將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></strong></span>呢句變成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日常問候語</span></strong></span><br />\n同埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道謝/Thank You嘅替代品</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月起每當我去便利店, 餐廳 ... 買野個D時候, 買完野我都會講句 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係所有人都有應我機，但都有不少人係會回我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最感動係返工個到有個看更啊叔，我次次收工都同佢講 光復香港，佢平時都會回我&quot;拜拜&quot;，但831之後，佢有日突然應我機，講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港&amp;時代革命</span></strong></span>唔止係口號同訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">係精神 係信念 <br />\n係文化 係生活</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家都可以養成呢個習慣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d1172fb9e81aeea156f8dbc8f68dace56c13c2a2","tid":1546251,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=269609ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"b99d7662f2ff2d84a6938cba7dfc16bdb6f81f37","tid":1546251,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bffcfa75005572dab522c56b3fa958d41fe3e66","tid":1546251,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a87236187b51fad9b620be688a6d9110780dbdd","tid":1546251,"uid":263219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"76473c837e633c9f3619c79cb6b19c8c70432ff2","tid":1546251,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c11b2043dc12bec014729a7a9bb16053ec1af388","tid":1546251,"uid":20552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a87236187b51fad9b620be688a6d9110780dbdd","tid":1546251,"uid":263219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"a50ddded842327f37f23b6c797431c86297831e4","tid":1546251,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"f5bc2412253795c1c9542d366f0bda7564dc9d6e","tid":1546251,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c11b2043dc12bec014729a7a9bb16053ec1af388","tid":1546251,"uid":20552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a87236187b51fad9b620be688a6d9110780dbdd","tid":1546251,"uid":263219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"全港連儂牆要人，文宣要人！<br />\n<br />\n8/9 美領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，全民都抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b5f42320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"848e663b7246f64b8442ba03b07215293ef99c03","tid":1546251,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"b09f174a1d12164b99b6156963d732c5e6f0b9af","tid":1546251,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b768b69710e920e696ac4dfae00146065eda08a9","tid":1546251,"uid":36420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25865c534447ee88e13b4b051818befde0359cbb","tid":1546251,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b768b69710e920e696ac4dfae00146065eda08a9","tid":1546251,"uid":36420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"呢句係用嚟問候黑警用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a49cc54b9aa78d9b0dcaa61cf4faea4df9f1b3","tid":1546251,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大個仔</span></span><span style=\"color: gold;\">獨立必睇</span></span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大核彈</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">內容包括</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">仲有！唔止 8.31晚，仲有 9.1 凌晨！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6122cdca38bf7e308ce005285e7f50bff3ed6384","tid":1546251,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"b98abb461373b6d724bbdcff5b74e1973cab2f80","tid":1546251,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"打招呼︰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span>(早晨=hello=Guten Morgen=bonjour=buenos d&iacute;as=おはよう=안녕)<br />\n<br />\n應機嗰個就答︰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b370687c3e35a8b5d5bfb252ccb8610cec1593c8","tid":1546251,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:2